OL,3,CGovernment policies 'creating' more
OL,4,Chomelessness, says Andy Burnham
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has said the government
OL,7,Fneeds to be more "radical" to end
OL,8,Fhomelessness, telling ITV News that
OL,9,Fthe Home Office and the Treasury are
OL,10,Fmaking the problem worse.
OL,12,FIn an exclusive interview ahead of the
OL,13,Fgovernment's publication of its long-
OL,14,Fawaited homelessness strategy, the
OL,15,FMayor of Greater Manchester called for
OL,16,Fa permanent return to the "everyone
OL,17,Fin" policy adopted during the
OL,18,Fpandemic, which saw the government
OL,19,Fhouse all rough sleepers to protect
OL,20,Fthem from the virus.
