OL,3,CGovernment policies 'creating' more
OL,4,Chomelessness, says Andy Burnham
OL,6,FBurnham vowed to end street
OL,7,Fhomelessness in Greater Manchester
OL,8,Fwhen he was elected in 2017, and since
OL,9,Fthen, rough sleeping has fallen by 42%.
OL,11,FHe said the region's 'Bed Every Night'
OL,12,Fpolicy is providing 600 rooms each
OL,13,Fnight for rough sleepers, but
OL,14,Fnationally, there wasn't funding to
OL,15,Fsustain it.
OL,17,F"I really feel the right thing to do
OL,18,Fas we go into the next phase of this
OL,19,FLabour government is to go back to
OL,20,F'everyone in'," he told ITV News.
