OL,6,F"That's what a 'Bed Every Night is',
OL,7,For what it's trying to be, it's harder
OL,8,Ffor us to sustain it, though, when
OL,9,Fthere isn't funding in homelessness
OL,10,Facross the whole of the country. We've
OL,11,Fhad some funding, but not enough."
OL,13,FBurnham, a former Labour minister,
OL,14,Fblamed the government for "policies
OL,15,Fthat actually create" homelessness.
