OL,3,CGovernment policies 'creating' more
OL,4,Chomelessness, says Andy Burnham
OL,6,FHe singled out the chancellor's
OL,7,Fdecision to freeze housing benefit
OL,8,Flevels, and the Home Office's policy
OL,9,Fof evicting asylum seekers from their
OL,10,Faccommodation once they are given
OL,11,Fstatus to remain, with nowhere to go.
OL,13,F"It does feel that we are having to
OL,14,Fwork around some of the problems
OL,15,Fcreated for us by the Westminster
OL,16,Fsystem. And I'd say it to any
OL,17,Fgovernment of any colour," Burnham
OL,18,Fsaid.
