OL,6,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham
OL,7,Ftells Daniel Hewitt the task of
OL,8,Fsolving homelessness 'has not been
OL,9,Fmade any easier by the actions of the
OL,10,FHome Office' in dealing with asylum
OL,11,Fseekers and refugees
OL,13,FHe also attacked the decision by the
OL,14,FLabour government to freeze local
OL,15,Fhousing allowance, which sets the
OL,16,Famount renters receive in housing
OL,17,Fbenefit, until at least 2026. Private
OL,18,Frents are rising, but freezing housing
OL,19,Fallowance means more and more
OL,20,Fproperties become increasingly
OL,21,Faffordable.
