OL,6,F"The Westminster world, because
OL,7,Fsometimes they pose as tough on
OL,8,Fbenefits, (says): 'let's freeze local
OL,9,Fhousing allowance'," Burnham said.
OL,11,F"All that means is families in private
OL,12,Frented accommodation see a growing gap
OL,13,Fbetween the rent that being have to
OL,14,Fpay and the level of support they're
OL,15,Fgetting from the system, and it gets
OL,16,Fbigger to the point where they're made
OL,17,Fhomeless and they have to present to
OL,18,Fthe council.
