OL,3,CGovernment policies 'creating' more
OL,4,Chomelessness, says Andy Burnham
OL,6,F"If you go for that 'housing first'
OL,7,Fapproach, 'Everyone in', a 'Bed Every
OL,8,FNight', those type of approaches, in
OL,9,Fthe end, in my view, you save money.
OL,10,FAnd that's what I would encourage them
OL,11,Fto do. So I'm not saying they haven't
OL,12,Fdone lots of good things. They have
OL,13,Fdone lots of really important things.
OL,14,FBut from here, let's get into a more
OL,15,Fradical approach.
