OL,3,CGovernment policies 'creating' more
OL,4,Chomelessness, says Andy Burnham
OL,6,F"I realise the pressures on the
OL,7,Fgovernment, but there's a big national
OL,8,Fshift the government said it wants to
OL,9,Fsee in the ten-year health plan,
OL,10,Fmoving from treatment to prevention.
OL,11,FThis is the perfect policy.
OL,13,F"If you end rough sleeping, you are
OL,14,Ftaking major steps to improve people's
OL,15,Fphysical and mental health and put
OL,16,Fthem on a path to recovery. And I
OL,17,Fthink that's what we should be
OL,18,Fcommitting to as a country."
