OL,6,FAnnouncing the strategy, Housing
OL,7,FSecretary Steve Reed said,
OL,8,F"Homelessness is one of the most
OL,9,Fprofound challenges we face as a
OL,10,Fsociety, because at the heart, it's
OL,11,Fabout people. Families deserve
OL,12,Fstability, childrenneed a safe place
OL,13,Fto grow, and individualssimply want
OL,14,Fthe dignity of a home.
OL,16,FThis strategy is shaped by the voices
OL,17,Fof those who've lived through
OL,18,Fhomelessness and the frontline workers
OL,19,Fwho fight tirelessly to prevent it.
